{"tid":1511700,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］重申獨立調查委員會嘅意義","createTime":"2019-08-27T15:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T03:53:37.000Z","uid":29545,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8a8bcbd5b57a17e0570f2acda852cd9a193c8122","tid":1511700,"uid":29545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:13:51.000Z","msg":"而家林鄭已經偷換咗獨立調查會同埋監警會嘅概念，希望模糊大家嘅焦點，麻煩大家同身邊嘅藍絲解釋返<br />\n<br />\n獨立調查委員會：<br />\n  反送中條例草案嘅基礎同埋推行方法有冇問題<br />\n  反送中事件發生嘅原因<br />\n  反送中遊行入面政府嘅行為同決定有冇問題<br />\n<br />\n監警會根本做唔到上面嘅三個function <br />\n唔該林鄭唔好再將監警會=獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可！</span>"},{"pid":"1a4e0e2354cf3d22a6c239aa342043b00c9e16f8","tid":1511700,"uid":29545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:14:03.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e288b6573e41b73049923e9d5f6f75ce979ce552","tid":1511700,"uid":29545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a9e561617933e1eee17c8f546a81e93a80af7bc","tid":1511700,"uid":29545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b369a72b0b1b74d07d30221fb24968286d16f273","tid":1511700,"uid":74818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:16:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5641f34eacb9644aa5f7c1918db0b57a4278a66b","tid":1511700,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:19:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>831民陣雙普選遊行</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6rpDtwf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6rpDtwf.png&h=9ea0b350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LRHQ4Da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLRHQ4Da.png&h=5bc14ba6&s={SIZE}\" />